    "Check for updates Zhenze Yang 1, 2, Weike Ye 1, Xiangyun Lei foot_0, Daniel Schweigert 1, Ha-Kyung Kwon 1 & Arash Khajeh 1 Solid polymer electrolytes offer promising advancements for next-generation batteries, boasting superior safety, enhanced specific energy, and extended lifespans over liquid electrolytes.",
    "However, low ionic conductivity and the vast polymer space hinder commercialization.",
